# Architecture Diagram

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    App[SwiftUI App Shell]
    App --> Commands[AppCommands / Menu Bar]
    App --> Window[MainWindowView]
    App --> Settings[Settings]

    Window --> Workspace[WorkspaceManager]
    Window --> Docs[DocumentManager]
    Window --> Editor[EditorViewModel]
    Window --> Session[SessionManager]
    Window --> Theme[ThemeManager]
    Window --> Quick[QuickSwitcher]

    Workspace --> Bookmarks[Security-Scoped Bookmarks]
    Workspace --> Tree[FileTreeBuilder]
    Workspace --> Index[FileIndexer]
    Workspace --> External[ExternalChangeMonitor]

    Docs --> FileService[FileService]
    Docs --> Buffers[DocumentBuffer]
    Docs --> Atomic[AtomicFileWriter]
    Docs --> Recovery[RecoveryBufferStore]

    Editor --> TextView[NSTextView Wrapper]
    TextView --> Storage[NSTextStorage]
    TextView --> Layout[NSLayoutManager]
    TextView --> Container[NSTextContainer]
    Editor --> Highlighter[MarkdownHighlighter]

    Session --> SessionJSON[latest-session.json]
    Recovery --> RecoveryJSON[recovery/buffer-uuid.json]
    Theme --> ThemeDefs[Built-in Themes]
    Settings --> Defaults[UserDefaults / AppStorage]
```
